print-ease (0.1.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix scanner discovery for printers with self-signed eSCL certificates
    (e.g. Ricoh, Canon, HP AirPrint devices on Ubuntu/Debian where CUPS
    auto-registers them with ipps:// URIs).
  * Upgrade scanner discovery failure log from DEBUG to WARNING for
    better visibility.

 -- MrHaku81 <haku81.kk@gmail.com>  Sun, 03 May 2026 15:30:00 +0200

